_[Listao [es]](http://www.listao.com.ar/2010/06/social-media-day-buenos-
aires-2010/)_ shares that on June 30, the [official Social Media
day](http://mashable.com/2010/06/08/join-mashable-in-celebrating-social-media-
day/), social media users are invited to get together to celebrate the day in
Buenos Aires. Users can sign up on a special site for the event on [Mashable
Meetups [es]](http://www.meetup.com/Mashable/7643/).

